data.title: Citylife in Rugeley and Cannock Chase September October 2022
data.meta_description: As September turns to October, the nights start to draw in, the leaves change colour and start to fall and so begins the wonderful season of Autumn! Our September and October edition magazine is full of our usual features to keep you entertained: recipes, competitions, history features, local news, What's On events and also lots of ideas for the best places to shop, eat and drink. So make yourself a warming latte, cut a slice of pumpkin pie and enjoy reading our special Autumnal edition of Citylife in Rugeley and Cannock Chase!
data.text:

So make yourself a warming latte, cut a slice of pumpkin pie and enjoy reading our special Autumnal edition of Citylife in Rugeley and Cannock Chase!
